This is the complete source code for Chapter 6 of Real-Time Web Application Development with Vert.x.



To run the application, type:

    vertx run app.js



Then point your web browser to http://localhost:8080

The files included:
* app.js - The deployment verticle
* mindmaps.js - Mind map management verticle
* mindmap_editor.js - Mind map editor verticle
* web/index.html - The application's HTML host page
* web/client.js - The client-side code of the application
* web/editor.js - The client-side code for the mind map editor
* web/mindmap_utils.js - Mindmap utility functions, shared between client and server
* web/style.css - Application stylesheet
* mods/com.vertxbook~mod-svg2png~1.0/mod.json - svg2png module descriptor
* mods/com.vertxbook~mod-svg2png~1.0/PNGExporter.java - svg2png module's main (and only) verticle
* mods/com.vertxbook~mod-svg2png~1.0/lib/*.jar - Java libraries (mainly Apache Batik) used by svg2png
* Vagrantfile - Vagrant configuration for the Ubuntu virtual machine used for deployment
* deploy.sh - A shell script for deploying the application
